***********
FEATURES
***********
Qt4 OSS 4.1 Mixer
System Tray support
Tested only on ArchLinux with Realtek ALC880 audio card

See CHANGELOG ...

***********
REPOSITORY
***********
http://github.com/antico/osso/tree/master

***********
DOWNLOAD
***********
- on first installation: "git clone git://github.com/antico/osso.git"
- to update your local repository: "git pull"

*************
INSTALLATION
*************
To compile, enter in "Osso" dir (where is the osso.pro) and type on shell:
"qmake" (or qmake-qt4)
"make"
---------------------------------------------------
To install, type on shell (as root):
"sh install"
---------------------------------------------------
To uninstall, type on shell (as root):
"sh uninstall"
---------------------------------------------------
To hide debug messages, uncomment in osso.pro
//DEFINES = QT_NO_DEBUG_OUTPUT
---------------------------------------------------
